dlxs::genSliceBar()

Description
    public string dlxs::genSliceBar(object $xml, string $file)
    Takes xml values and places them into a template.

Parameters
    xml
    	An xml file containing the start, end, and total values in the form of $xml->SliceSummary->Start, $xml->SliceSummary->End, and$xml->SliceSummary->Total respectively.
    file
    	A file containing markup.

Return Values
    A string in the format of the template file with start, end, and total values placed into it.

Examples
    <?
    ...
    print $dlxs->genSliceBar($xml,"/path/to/template.php");
    ...
    ?>

Notes
	This function makes use of the dlxs::buildTemplate() function, therefore looping is possible if desired.
   
See Also
	dlxs::buildTemplate()